      <span class="k-coord">/AGENTS.02 · BLUEBOOK 22E · COURTLISTENER</span>
    </div>
    <div class="head-row">
      <div>
        <h1 class="head-title">Every cite, <em>verified</em>.</h1>
        <p class="head-sub">Upload a brief, motion, or memorandum. The agent extracts every citation, classifies each one against the Bluebook 22nd Edition, runs the table validators, checks each case against CourtListener, and emits a tracked-changes redline plus a sign-off-ready form-check report.</p>
      </div>
