        I understand this is an AI-assisted form-check tool, not legal services or legal advice. No attorney-client
        relationship is formed by uploading. The report records Bluebook 22e form-checking <strong>only</strong> and
        does NOT attest to the substantive accuracy of any cited authority. Existence checks use CourtListener, which
        does not include every state opinion, recent unpublished disposition, or sealed matter. I am responsible for
        independently verifying every citation before filing, and for ensuring my use of this tool complies with my
        own confidentiality and competence obligations under the rules of professional conduct in my jurisdiction.
        See the <a href="/legal/disclaimer/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Disclaimer</a>,
        <a href="/legal/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Privacy Policy</a>,
        and <a href="/legal/terms/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Terms</a>.
        <em>(disclaimer v1.1)</em>
